<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="belief-n">belief <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'liːf/    美 /bɪ'liːf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 相信；信任：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I haven’t much <strong>belief in</strong> his honesty. 
我不大相信他是诚实的。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] [可用单数] 信念；看法：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One traditional belief about television is that it reduces a child’s ability to think. 
关于电视的一个传统看法是它降低了儿童的思维能力。</p><footer>2015 广东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Many people hold <strong>a firm / strong belief that</strong> the cure for cancer will be found one day.
很多人坚信总有一天能找到治愈癌症的方法。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] [常用复数] 信仰；信条：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>religious beliefs 
宗教信仰</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Increases in bear sightings around human settlements have led to a ______(believe) that polar bear populations are increasing.  （2019 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. belief  </p></div>